Whether these gloves actually confer upon the wielder an actual link with their diety is a subject of heated debate in the Temple of Cordor and around Kohlingen.  

Yet invariably, they do seem to aid their wearer nonetheless.

These rings are rumored to be more plant than metal, with the shape consisting of fine interlapping vines. 

There are stories of those particularly experienced with these rings able to reshape them into entangling plant-life, and whether or not mere fables, it does lead some credence to the overall shape of these rings.
